1. *Vodim* se za njenim glasom. (I follow her voice.)
2. *Vodi* me do tvojih očiju. (Lead me to your eyes.)
3. *Vodila* me je kroz život. (She led me through life.)
4. *Vodio* sam te do zvezda. (I guided you to the stars.)
5. *Vodeći* se po vetaru, leteli smo daleko. (Following the wind, we flew far away.)